so I got to sell
a hundred and one.

605
00:20:41,532 --> 00:20:42,617
I must kill.

606
00:20:42,700 --> 00:20:44,118
With that in mind,

607
00:20:44,202 --> 00:20:46,371
I am going to read to you
the jokes handed to me

608
00:20:46,454 --> 00:20:49,540
