comedy writers this morning.

609
00:20:49,624 --> 00:20:50,917
I'd like your opinion.

610
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,669
We are here for you, Danny.
Right, boys?

611
00:20:52,752 --> 00:20:54,337
- Midge?
- Hell no.

