636
00:21:42,844 --> 00:21:44,220
Oh, great. Homework. Thanks.

637
00:21:44,303 --> 00:21:46,055
Excuse me, Danny?
Gordon's ready for you.

638
00:21:46,139 --> 00:21:48,558
Thank you, sweetheart.
Kids, find me some jokes.

