the second time.

646
00:22:02,947 --> 00:22:07,994
Across the board on the math,
English, science, logic.

647
00:22:08,077 --> 00:22:10,246
But he did spell his name
correctly this time,

648
00:22:10,329 --> 00:22:12,057
