739
00:25:27,735 --> 00:25:29,278
"Hey, what's flammable here?"

740
00:25:29,362 --> 00:25:30,988
That's terrible.

741
00:25:31,072 --> 00:25:33,050
They strapped everything
they owned onto their backs

742
00:25:33,074 --> 00:25:35,284
