759
00:26:04,855 --> 00:26:05,982
Too Jewish.

760
00:26:08,192 --> 00:26:09,235
Finally get out,

761
00:26:09,318 --> 00:26:10,903
move to a tenement on Delancey,

762
00:26:10,987 --> 00:26:13,155
